step_ValuesTable.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceOmniAgentWork_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'Status' in ["Canceled", "Closed"]; q = foreach q generate 'Name' as 'Name','Case_CaseNumber' as 'Case_CaseNumber', 'Case_Account_Name' as 'Case_Account_Name','UserId_Name' as 'UserId_Name','SpeedToAnswer' as 'SpeedToAnswer', 'HandleTime' as 'HandleTime','ActiveTime' as 'ActiveTime','Case_Origin' as 'Case_Origin','Group_Name' as 'Group_Name','Status' as 'Status', 'Case_Product_Family_KB__c' as 'Case_Product_Family_KB__c';q = limit q 100;

query.pigql: a = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceOmniAgentWork_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";a = filter a by 'Status' in ["Canceled", "Closed"];a = group a by ('RequestDateTime_Year','RequestDateTime_Month','RequestDateTime_Day','RequestDateTime_Hour');a = foreach a generate 'RequestDateTime_Year'+"~~~"+'RequestDateTime_Month'+"~~~"+'RequestDateTime_Day' as 'each_date', 'RequestDateTime_Hour' as 'RequestDateTime_Hour', count() as 'date_hour_volume', unique('UserId_Name') as 'date_hour_agents_working' ;a= group a by 'RequestDateTime_Hour';a = foreach a generate 'RequestDateTime_Hour' as 'RequestDateTime_Hour', round(sum('date_hour_volume')/unique('each_date'),0) as 'Request Volume', round(sum('date_hour_agents_working')/unique('each_date'),0) as '# Agents Working';a = order a by ('RequestDateTime_Hour' asc)
